      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">The main change is that sales periods are now compared like-for-like. This gives you a fairer and more accurate view of your performance.</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">​</span></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">For example, sales from &quot;Today&quot; up to the current time are compared against sales from &quot;Yesterday&quot; up to the </span><em style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">exact same time</em><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">.</span></li></ul>",
