      "step_title": "Today",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Current Period: Sales from today (midnight 00:00 to the current time).</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Compared Against: Sales from yesterday (midnight 00:00 to the </span><em style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">exact same current time</em><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\"> as today).</span></li></ul><p></p>",
