      "step_order": 5,
      "step_title": "This Week",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Current Period: Sales from the start of this week (Sunday at midnight 00:00) up to the current day and time.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Compared Against: Sales from last week (Sunday at midnight 00:00 up to the </span><em style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">same day and time as the current moment this week</em><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">).</span></li></ul>",
