      "step_order": 6,
      "step_title": "This Month",
      "content": "<ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Current Period: Sales from the 1st of this month (at midnight 00:00) up to the current date and time.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Compared Against: Sales from the 1st of last month (at midnight 00:00) up to the </span><em style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">same date and time in that previous month</em><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">.</span></li></ul>",
