      "step_title": "Benefits of This Updated Comparison Method",
      "content": "<p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">This new way of comparing your sales figures helps you because:</span></p><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">It&#39;s More Accurate: You get a true side-by-side comparison.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">You See Real-Time Trends Better: Understand how your business is performing right now compared to the same point in the previous period.</span></li></ul><p></p><ul><li><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(26, 26, 26);\">Make Smarter Decisions: Use this clearer information to guide your business choices.</span></li></ul>",
